# All Bittensor subnet knowledge is in @knowledge/
# Start with @knowledge/INDEX.yaml for task routing

# PwnTensor-specific context:
# - This is a game AI subnet where miners compete to build ghost AI for PacTensor
# - Validators run headless game sims and serve the frontend
# - The scoring function rewards "fun" ghost AI (challenging but fair)
# - protocol.py defines GameStateSynapse (validator->miner game state, miner->validator ghost actions)
# - reward.py defines the fun-score calculation and rank normalization
# - frontend/index.html is the playable PacTensor game

# Quick reference:
# - ALWAYS load subnet.invariants.yaml first (non-negotiable rules)
# - Use design_flow.yaml to select mechanism pattern
# - Pattern files: compute_auction, capacity_market, data_indexing,
#   prediction_market, time_series_forecasting, external_activity_verification,
#   adversarial_red_blue, container_execution

